<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Clownodex</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/main.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to the Clownodex</h1>
        <p>We don't miss the circus, but we sure do miss the clowns.</p>
        <% if (!user) { %>
        <a href="/auth/register" class="cta-button">Register Here</a>
        <a href="/auth/sign-in" class="cta-button">Sign In</a>
        <% } else { %>
            <p>Welcome, <%= user.username %>!</p>
            <a href="/auth/sign-out" class="cta-button">Sign Out</a>
        <% } %>
    </header>

    <section id="stay-in-touch">
        <h2>Stay in touch with the clowns from your life!</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>An organized database helping you stay in touch with those who matter.</li>
            <li>Don't let people fade out of your life! Key features to help you stay in contact regularly.</li>
            <li>Add customizable notes and never forget what's going in their lives!</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
      <!-- Insert the image from the local directory -->
      <div class="img-container">
      <img src="/images/clownsgroup.jpg" alt="Group of clowns" class="img-clowns">
      </div>
    <section id="simple-to-use">
        <h2>Simple to Use</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Create an account to get started.</li>
            <li>Add and manage contacts effortlessly.</li>
            <li>Easy search and filter options.</li>
        </ol>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Clownodex</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
